moves.name: Fire Bow
moves.notes: arrow lasts 30 frames minimum (if it doesnrt hit ground), 13 rames startup and 25 frames endlag upon release

moves.name: Boomerang
moves.notes: 20 frames to catch the boomerang.

moves.name: Bomb
moves.notes: bomb pulled out on frame 16. able to start throwing on frame 40. bomb has multipule hitboxes, unknown how much each does (damage listed assumes all hits land)

moves.name: Up Smash
moves.notes: 4 hits, first hit frames 11-14 and does 3% and 3 frames shield stun. second hit frames 26-28 and does 2% damage and 2 frames shield stun. third hit frames 40-42 can do 7 or 8% damage and 5 frames shield stun. last hit frames 43-44 and can do 8 or 9% damage and 5 or 6 frames shield stun

moves.name: Down Smash
moves.notes: front hit frames 9-11, does 13% or 7% damage. back hit frames 21-23, does 12% or 6% damage

moves.name: Neutral Air
moves.notes: weak hit frames 6-27

moves.name: Forward Air
moves.notes: first hit frames 14-16, does 12%, 11%, or 9% damage. Second hit frames 17-33, does 8%, 7%, or 5% damage with 5 frames shield stun

moves.name: Down Air
moves.notes: meteor hitbox frames 16-64

moves.name: Spin Attack
moves.notes: x amount of 1% hitboxes followed by 3% hitbox

moves.name: Rapid Jabs
moves.notes: rapid jab has an additional 7 frames of startup and 10 fames of endlag

moves.name: Spin Attack (Air)
moves.notes: x amount of 1% hitboxes followed by 3% hitbox

moves.name: Grab

moves.name: Dashgrab
moves.notes: Close grab is frame 14-15, hook is frame 14-17.
